title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) per capita in the Philippines 2024
yAxis: GDP per capita in U.S. dollars
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes GDP per capita in U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 41.
Overall GDP per capita in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2023 and 2024.
Maximum GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, about 4673.78 was reported at Year 2024
The lowest GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, of value 597.84 was reported at Year 1986
